            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>In the fall after we returned home from the Family History Mission, we got a telephone call from my daughter who was living in England with her family at that time. She said, “Mom, do you and Dad think that you might want to serve another mission?” 


