            <span id="ChapterParagraphTwo">
            
               When we were just about ready to have our first meeting in one of the homes in the area, Kenneth said, “I'm going to call the Briggs again on the telephone and see if they're home, rather than make a visit.” 
 
            </span>

            <span id="SEE_MORE"><a href="#" id="restofstory3-show"  onclick="showHide('restofstory3');return false;">SEE MORE</a>
