            <span id="textspanlichapter22">ALICE CHAU</span><br /><span id="textspanlichapter24">SISTER</span>
            </span-->

            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>Another idea that we had to encourage our little grandsons to serve missions was to start a missionary fund for them. I found a missionary bank at the Deseret Book Store, and for each of my great-grandsons, I put a $50 bill in that bank and gave it to them on one of their birthdays. Then each birthday I added a little money to that to encourage our great-grandsons to plan for missions.
            </span>

            <!--div id="ChapterPictureGallery" class="clearfix">
